data.description: Luxurious John Weiland built three story END UNIT townhome with ELEVATOR in sought after gated WESTON swim/tennis community. NEW KITCHEN, NEW HICKORY HARDWOODS ON MAIN. 10 ft ceilings on main. Gorgeous fenced backyard with NEW COMPOSITE DECK.  Pristine white kitchen with Quartz counters, soft close cabinets, Burnished Gold sink and faucet, upgraded appliances including gas cooktop, built in oven and microwave. Refrigerator stays! Butlers pantry near formal dining room. All New lighting on main. Great view from kitchen, breakfast area and family room of backyard with gardens. Family room has fireplace with gas logs. Oversized Primary suite with Juliette balcony. Bath has jetted tub and large walk in shower, double vanities and two closets with custom organizers. Additional large bedroom on 2nd floor. 3rd floor media room with wet bar and separate bedroom or home office with French Doors. This home has been lovingly maintained and upgraded. Extra storage and Epoxy floors in garage. Gas line for grill in backyard. Grill stays too! 4 new toilets, 2 are self cleaning. These homes rarely go on the market, especially with an end unit and elevator. Hurry to make this home!
